Title: Tactical Withdrawal
Description:
We have stopped this attack on the barrier, but Fyrakk will find a way through.

$n, we need to return to Alexstrasza and Merithra and tell them his plans for the Wellspring.

Return as soon as possible. It is more urgent than ever to stop Fyrakk.
ObjectivesText: Return to Alexstrasza in the Central Encampment.
